Portugal continental recommendation

This a project based on foursquare infomation regarding the boroughs in Portugal into groups.

The boroughs were take from https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lista_de_munic%C3%ADpios_de_Portugal_por_popula%C3%A7%C3%A3o using the requests and BeautifulSoup library.

The districits were taken using Nominatim library and using the boroughs.

The venues category uses Fourquare to take the Top 10 Most common venues displayed into categories based on their frequency.

The KMeans is the library used to group the boroughs into cluster based on their Most common venues.

The folium Map is used to plot the places using the latitude and longitude.
